Go to the settings page and add your OpenAI API or GroqAI API key.
Add your UEX API for commodities and items.
Add your Supabase anon key and project URL.
Enable toggle on Supabase AI mode.

This will give you access to all StarCitizen items, along with an AI agent to help you locate items more easily.

Supabase is used to reduce API token usage. Without it, a single query may use around 17,000 tokens.
